    Chat Overlay Script (Messenger-style bubble)
    Execute as a LocalScript via executor.

    Features:
    - Login screen to set display name (name#XXXX)
    - Draggable floating bubble pinned to screen edge
    - Expandable chat panel with polished UI
    - 20-second send cooldown
    - Reply-to feature with mention highlighting
    - Settings to change name (re-randomizes #number)
    - Server-only messages (no client-side faking)
    - Auto-refresh via game:HttpGet every cycle
]]

